%MicrosoftSQL
select 
count(1) AS Claims_Count, sum(CLCL_TOT_CHG) AS Total_Charge, sum(CLCL_TOT_PAYABLE) AS Total_Payable,
CLCL_CUR_STS, CLCL_INPUT_DT, CSCS_ID, CSPI_ID, PDPD_ID, GRGR_CK, NWPR_PFX, NWNW_ID
from fabncpr0..CMC_CLCL_CLAIM 
WHERE 
CLCL_CUR_STS IN (01,02) AND
CSPD_CAT IN ('M') AND
CLCL_INPUT_DT > '07-01-2017'
GROUP BY
CLCL_CUR_STS, CLCL_INPUT_DT, CSCS_ID, CSPI_ID, PDPD_ID, GRGR_CK, NWPR_PFX, NWNW_ID--, CLCL_TOT_CHG, CLCL_TOT_PAYABLE
ORDER BY
CLCL_INPUT_DT
